  "_note": "B2 Decision Intelligence policy — §28 materiality weights, band thresholds, token detectors, and routine ceiling (BIZ-0001 / WF-0037 / ADR-0125). Editing any weight or threshold is an ADR act (constitution §9). Modules: runtime/execution/materiality-score.mjs, runtime/execution/decision-need-classifier.mjs.",
